snippet.textDisplay: The House of Representatives has had all the time they needed (or wanted) to call for witnesses during both Mr. Shiff's and Mr. Nadler's investigations. Overall, I felt there was a serious mischaracterization by Mr. Shiff of the real facts and words said during the call by the President of the United States to the leader of the Ukraine.
